* [[承德勿忘草|承德勿忘草]]{{sname|''Myosotis bothriospermoides''}}
* [[湿地勿忘草|湿地勿忘草]]{{sname|''Myosotis caespitosa''}}
* [[细根勿忘草|细根勿忘草]]{{sname|''Myosotis krylovii''}}
